{
    "name":  "1A - GBP Publisher (Daily Gate)",
    "nodes":  [
                  {
                      "parameters":  {
                                         "content":  "## 1A — GBP Publisher (Daily Gate)\n\n**Schedule:** Daily 09:00 IST\n\n**Prerequisites:**\n1. Set n8n variables: `CRM_API_URL`, `CRM_API_KEY`, `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN`, `TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID`, `ADMIN_EMAIL`\n2. Create credentials:\n   - `CRM API Auth` (Header Auth): Name=`Authorization`, Value=`Bearer YOUR_CRM_API_KEY`\n   - `OpenAI API Key` (Header Auth): Name=`Authorization`, Value=`Bearer sk-YOUR_KEY`\n   - `Google Business Profile` (OAuth2)\n3. Replace `CHANGE_ME_*` credential IDs after import\n4. Set `GBP_ACCOUNT_ID` and `GBP_LOCATION_ID` in variables\n\n**Flow:** Cron → Fetch content → Combo check → OpenAI 6 variants → Save payload → Publish GBP → Log result",
                                         "height":  340,
                                         "width":  860,
                                         "color":  4
                                     },
                      "id":  "1a000000-0001-4000-8000-000000000001",
                      "name":  "📋 Setup Instructions",
                      "type":  "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
                      "typeVersion":  1,
                      "position":  [
                                       -60,
                                       -80
                                   ]
                  },
                  {
                      "parameters":  {
                                         "rule":  {
